headline: Two Reasons to Like MTCH (and One Not So Much)
summary: While the S&P 500 is up 14% since June 2024, Match Group (currently trading at $32.74 per share) has lagged behind, posting a return of 5.5%. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
